Dr.Vijayaprabha is such a caring and amazing dentist. She is extremely friendly and patient. She takes utmost care of her patients. I had visited the clinic for the first time when my son was 1 year old for his tooth decay treatment. She knows how to talk and handle the children in a way that builds trust and make the child feel ease & comfortable. Even after shifting my home far from the clinic location, I have been visiting the doctor for all dental problems of my family members. Its been 7 years I have been visiting the doctor as we didn't feel comfortable and confident with other corporate dental clinics.

She clearly understands the root of the problem and starts the treatment swiftly.  The clinic is very well maintained and neat. I can't thank enough for her support, care, kindness & patience through my experience.  Visiting doctors are also very much patient friendly. In my experience, she never asked for unnecessary visits/treatments. She manages the appointments very well and never made us for more than 10-15 mins. Above all, she used to give multiple wellness tips to maintain oral hygiene & to avoid tooth decay. Its really difficult to find a doctor nowadays who gives tips to avoid/minimize the visits. She is genuine & the most incredible dentist I have ever seen. 

I strongly recommend my friends, family & neighbors to visit Dr. Vijayaprabha. Thank for you mam for being what you are!

Dr. Vijay Prabha (Smile Dental Clinic) 
Thanks a million to the dentist & classmate, who restored my smile. 
It was a very long, weary and challenging task of many RCTs & crowns. Also, I got my wisdom teeth removed surgically, got few RCTs and crowns for my upper front teeth. They have a good surgeon for surgical procedures, and the rest of the work were performed by Dr Vijaya Prabha, who took extreme care in performing the procedure. She is very open to patients' feedback, and took our concerns into consideration while making the anterior crowns. The clinic is very friendly and wants satisfaction from patients foremost.
Dr.Prabha and Dr. Suganya are very friendly and handles their patients with the at most care and are always available for help. Will surely recommend.
